Sentencas: A 10 mol%Sc2O3, 1 mol%CeO2 stabilized-ZrO2 (SSZ) powder was successfully prepared using the sol gel method.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Subsequent SSZ electrolyte pellets were prepared by tape casting technique and sintered at 1400 degrees C, 1450 degrees C, 1500 degrees C, 1550 degrees C and 1600 degrees C. These were characterized by X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS).
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: SSZ showed a pure cubic phase after sintering, the grain size of SSZ increased with the increase of sintering temperature.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The SSZ sintered at 1550 degrees C showed the highest ion conductivity.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power densities of Ni-SSZ/SSZ/La0.8Sr0.2MnO3-delta (LSM)-SSZ single cells sintered at 1550 degrees C were 0.18, 0.36, 0.51 and 0.72 W cm(-2) at 650, 700, 750 and 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The polarization resistance (R-p) of the single cell attained 0.201 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C. (C) 2016 Elsevier Ltd and Techna Group S.r.l.
Titulo: Fabrication and characterization of SSZ tape cast electrolyte-supported solid oxide fuel cells
